				.page-content
					h3 Trust and Estate Tax Planning
					p Our trust and estate planning practice concentrates on using innovative planning techniques to fulfill our clientsâ€™ dispositive goals and to reduce and eliminate taxes. We assist our clients in planning trusts and estates, conveying the family owned corporations and other business interests to children, making charitable donations, and administering their trusts and estates.

			.page-container
				.sidebar
					h4 How we can help
					ul
						li Drafting Contracts and Agreement
						li Entity Selection and Formation
						li Business Immigration (H -1B, L-1, E-2, Green Card, etc)
				.page-content
					h3 Business and Immigration
					p A successful business depends largely upon careful preparation and operation of business with appropriate legal advice. We assist our clients on every aspect of their business, ranging from drafting agreements on day-to-day operation to handling their immigration matters.

